version of Aftereffects last night.

00:02:46.870 --> 00:02:47.870
&gt;&gt;Galpin: Yeah?

00:02:47.870 --> 00:02:52.770
&gt;&gt;Ni-Lewis: So if I get some time over the
weekend, who knows what amazing things might

00:02:52.770 --> 00:02:53.770
happen?

00:02:53.770 --> 00:02:55.110
&gt;&gt;Galpin: There might be some amazing, cool
stuff.

